resultObject.appInstanceSql: select tb2.grid_no as grid_no,SUM(tb1.flux) as flux_sum12,SUM(CASE WHEN ( ( ( tb1.channel_id > 1 and tb3.lan_id > 1 ) ) ) THEN tb1.flux ELSE 0 END) as flux_sum3,SUM(CASE WHEN ( ( ( tb3.is_boutique = '1' and tb3.lan_id > 1 ) ) ) THEN tb1.flux ELSE 0 END) as flux_sum,SUM(CASE WHEN ( ( ( tb3.lan_id > 1 and tb3.team_id > '1' ) ) ) THEN tb1.flux ELSE 0 END) as flux_sum7,SUM(CASE WHEN ( ( ( tb1.channel_id > 1 and tb3.team_id > '1' ) ) ) THEN tb1.flux ELSE 0 END) as flux_sum4,SUM(CASE WHEN ( ( ( tb1.user_id > 1 and tb3.channel_id > 1 ) ) ) THEN tb1.flux ELSE 0 END) as flux_sum11,SUM(CASE WHEN ( ( ( tb3.lan_id > 1 and tb3.lan_id > 1 ) ) ) THEN tb1.flux ELSE 0 END) as flux_sum6,SUM(CASE WHEN ( ( ( tb1.user_id > 1 and tb3.lan_id > 1 ) ) ) THEN tb1.flux ELSE 0 END) as flux_sum9,SUM(CASE WHEN ( ( ( tb3.is_boutique = '1' and tb3.team_id > '1' ) ) ) THEN tb1.flux ELSE 0 END) as flux_sum1,SUM(CASE WHEN ( ( ( tb1.user_id > 1 and tb3.team_id > '1' ) ) ) THEN tb1.flux ELSE 0 END) as flux_sum10,SUM(CASE WHEN ( ( ( tb1.channel_id > 1 and tb3.channel_id > 1 ) ) ) THEN tb1.flux ELSE 0 END) as flux_sum5,SUM(CASE WHEN ( ( ( tb3.is_boutique = '1' and tb3.channel_id > 1 ) ) ) THEN tb1.flux ELSE 0 END) as flux_sum2,ROUND(IFNULL((SUM(tb1.flux)+SUM(tb1.flux)),0),2) as calculate495,SUM(CASE WHEN ( ( ( tb3.lan_id > 1 and tb3.channel_id > 1 ) ) ) THEN tb1.flux ELSE 0 END) as flux_sum8 from smart_test.USER tb1 inner join test.grid_list tb2 on tb1.area_id = tb2.grid_no inner join smart_test.channel tb3 on tb1.channel_id = tb3.channel_id where ( tb1.month_id ={acct} ) group by tb2.grid_no
